      <title>中国金融、房地产公司员工数量首次减少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-26/china-s-finance-property-firm-workforces-shrink-for-first-time</link>
      <description><![CDATA[近年来，中国金融和房地产公司的员工数量首次出现萎缩，反映出房地产市场崩溃和监管调查所造成的损害。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-26/china-s-finance-property-firm-workforces-shrink-for-first-time</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Dec 2024 09:26:33 GMT</pubDate>
